text:
Like most I'm busy during the week to keep a roof over my head, but I want to find that special someone I can enjoy weekends together with. This could be anything; exploring unknown parts of Los Angeles, hiking, bike riding the beach strand, driving up the coast, diner and a movie, laying out by the pool on a mini vacation to the desert etc.

I'm single, white, in my 50's, strong, active, non-judge mental and seeking someone to smile and enjoy happy times with. All I ask is that you are drug and disease free (420 is cool) and a responsible person.

If you're interested in knowing more please respond with this information about yourself:

Age;
Location;
Picture;
Your interest;

Please take the time to respond, no one liners. . .
